sequenceDiagram
    actor 사용자
    participant UI as 웹 UI
    participant Ctrl as FileUploadControl
    participant Perm as SharePermission
    participant File as FileItem
    participant Ver as FileVersion
    participant Storage as StorageService
    participant DB as Database
    participant Log as ActivityLog

    사용자->>UI: 파일 선택 후 업로드 요청
    UI->>Ctrl: upload(file, folderId, userId)
    Ctrl->>Perm: verifyUpload(userId, folderId)
    Perm-->>Ctrl: 권한 확인 결과
    Ctrl->>Storage: saveFile(file)
    Storage-->>Ctrl: storagePath 반환
    Ctrl->>File: upload(metadata)
    File->>DB: save()
    Ctrl->>Ver: create(versionNo, storagePath)
    Ver->>DB: save()
    Ctrl->>Log: record(UPLOAD)
    Ctrl-->>UI: 업로드 성공 응답
    UI-->>사용자: 파일 목록 갱신
